1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,520
The ball in the hole
球在洞里

2
00:00:03,140 --> 00:00:09,880
School is over.  Li Ming and Han Fei are going back home.
放学后  李明和韩菲正要回家

3
00:00:10,440 --> 00:00:16,820
Near the school gate they see a little boy.  He is crying.
在学校大门附近看见一个小男孩正在哭

4
00:00:17,340 --> 00:00:22,000
They go up to him and ask, “What’s wrong with you?”
他们走上前问  你怎么了

5
00:00:22,900 --> 00:00:26,980
The boy points to a hole in the ground and says,
小男孩指着地上的洞说

6
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:34,080
“My ball is in the hole and I can’t get it out.  Can you help me?”
我的球掉进洞里了  我拿不出来  你们能帮我吗

7
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:39,800
“Don’t worry,” says Li Ming. “We can help you.”
别担心  李明说  我们可以帮你

8
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:45,860
They look into the hole and try to take the ball out with their hands,
他们向洞里看  试着用手把球拿出来

9
00:00:46,620 --> 00:00:50,560
but they can’t because the hole is too deep.
但是因为洞太深了他们做不到

10
00:00:50,980 --> 00:00:57,220
They think and think.  Then Li Ming has an idea.
他们想了又想  李明有了个主意

11
00:00:57,980 --> 00:01:01,780
“We can use water,” he says.
我们可以用水  他说。

12
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:08,860
“Oh, yes!  That’s a good idea,” Han Fei says.
对呀  真是个好主意  韩非说

13
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:14,440
“Let’s go back to the school and get some water.”
我们回学校取点水吧

14
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:22,820
Soon they get some water and pour it into the hole, and the ball comes up.
不久他们拿来了水倒进洞里  球浮了上来

15
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:28,060
“Now we can get the ball,” says Han Fei.
现在我们可以拿到球了  韩非说道

16
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:32,720
She takes the ball out and gives it to the boy.
她把球拿出来给了那个男孩

17
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:38,380
The boy smiles and says, “Thank you very much.”
男孩笑着说  太感谢你们了

